snippet.title: Homing Missile
snippet.description:
Steer the plane to collect stars and avoid missiles.

 - Collects stars and unlock powerful planes.

- Control the plane with joystick and left/right buttons.

- Use Fire Button to Throw Flares.

- Shield and Speed boost power-ups.

-Compete with other players on Google Play Leaderboard
